Bulding process-->> compiling , linking and packaging of the code 

Maven : Maven is a build toool build by APACHE Foundation to build , publish and deploy multiple projects at once.
        Supports C#, Java, Ruby
        based on project object model
        takes care of builds, DEPENDANCIES , reports , releases, distribution, mailing lists

Graddle : build automation tool , 
          gradle does everything maven does and counter maven's shortcommings too 
